OL,3,CReview of airport policing recommended
OL,5,FInspectors also examined Belfast
OL,6,FHarbour Police in the report which
OL,7,Flooked at day-to-day policing
OL,8,Fundertaken by both organisations,
OL,9,Fwhich are separately funded and
OL,10,Foperated from the Police Service of
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland (PSNI).
OL,13,FChief Inspector Jacqui Durkin, said
OL,14,Fboth bodies should agree and sign a
OL,15,Fnew memorandum of understanding with
OL,16,Fthe PSNI within six months.
