OL,3,CReview of airport policing recommended
OL,5,FIt was also recommended that a
OL,6,Ffundamental review of policing at
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland's airports should be
OL,8,Fled by the PSNI in partnership with
OL,9,FBelfast International Airport
OL,10,FConstabulary and Belfast Harbour
OL,11,FPolice, who also look after Belfast
OL,12,FCity Airport, to be completed in the
OL,13,Fnext 18 months.
OL,15,FMs Durkin described Northern Ireland's
OL,16,Fairports and harbours as key entry and
OL,17,Fexit points for people, as well as
OL,18,Fimportant for the economy, business
OL,19,Fand trade.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/15
