OL,3,CReview of airport policing recommended
OL,5,F"Recent investment and ambitious
OL,6,Fexpansion plans means effective
OL,7,Fpolicing at these critical locations
OL,8,Fneeds to meet current and consider
OL,9,Ffuture needs," she said.
OL,11,F"This is crucial to maintain national
OL,12,Fsecurity, prevent and disrupt criminal
OL,13,Factivity and keep everyone safe who
OL,14,Flives, works at or visits them."
