OL,3,CReview of airport policing recommended
OL,5,FIn terms of the BIAC, Ms Durkin said
OL,6,Fthis was their first CJI inspection,
OL,7,Fand inspectors had been concerned by
OL,8,Fthe lack of appropriate police-
OL,9,Fexperienced leadership as well as gaps
OL,10,Fin existing accountability
OL,11,Farrangements and consistency in
OL,12,Foperational delivery and outcomes.
OL,14,FShe said they were also concerned by
OL,15,Fits existing rank structure.
OL,17,FBIAC works along with the PSNI, UK
OL,18,FBorder Force, Home Office and Revenue
OL,19,Fand Customs at its Aldergrove site.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/15
