OL,3,CReview of airport policing recommended
OL,5,F"We have recommended that within the
OL,6,Fnext six months Belfast International
OL,7,FAirport Constabulary should develop a
OL,8,Fvision, strategy and policing plan to
OL,9,Fdirect policing at the airport that
OL,10,Faddresses these issues and aligns with
OL,11,Fthe current PSNI Policing Plan
OL,12,Fpriorities," Ms Durkin said.
OL,14,F"We have had positive discussions with
OL,15,Fsenior management at Belfast
OL,16,FInternational Airport about the
OL,17,Finspection findings and inspection
OL,18,Freport publication and I acknowledge
OL,19,Ftheir commitment to secure policing
OL,20,Fimprovements that are needed in the
OL,21,Fshort and longer term.
OL,26,@mD@AOUtD@LO]vD@AOU
