OL,3,CReview of airport policing recommended
OL,5,F"I also welcome the development of an
OL,6,Faction plan by Belfast International
OL,7,FAirport to underpin the implementation
OL,8,Fof the accepted inspection
OL,9,Frecommendations."
OL,11,FMeanwhile, inspectors found that
OL,12,FBelfast Harbour Police benefited from
OL,13,Fpolice-experienced leadership,
OL,14,Fappropriate accountability and that
OL,15,Frobust governance arrangements were in
OL,16,Foperation.
OL,26,@mD@AOUqD@QO]
