OL,3,CReview of airport policing recommended
OL,5,F"Belfast Harbour Police was a trusted
OL,6,Fpartner of the PSNI where a mutually
OL,7,Fbeneficial, professional relationship
OL,8,Fhad developed and was maintained," Ms
OL,9,FDurkin said.
OL,11,F"Belfast Harbour Police officers also
OL,12,Fhad access to appropriate information
OL,13,Fand continuous police training that
OL,14,Fensured they had the knowledge and
OL,15,Fexpertise to operate to national
OL,16,Fstandards.
OL,26,@mD@AOUpD@bO]sD@AOU
