OL,3,CReview of airport policing recommended
OL,5,F"While we welcome this positive
OL,6,Frelationship, inspectors have
OL,7,Frecommended the policing priorities of
OL,8,Fthe Belfast Harbour Police should be
OL,9,Fmore aligned with those set by the
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland Policing Board and
OL,11,Fthe PSNI."
OL,13,FMs Durkin said that both police
OL,14,Fservices should also begin discussions
OL,15,Fwith the Public Prosecution Service
OL,16,Ffor Northern Ireland to move to a
OL,17,Fdigital case planning and submission
OL,18,Fprocess for criminal case files in
OL,19,Fkeeping with the current digital
OL,20,Fjustice strategy.
OL,26,@mD@AOUsD@JO]
