OL,5,FAdditionally, she called for work be
OL,6,Fundertaken by the Department of
OL,7,FJustice to prepare for legislative
OL,8,Fchange within the next Northern
OL,9,FIreland Assembly mandate to extend the
OL,10,Fpowers of both police services, when
OL,11,Frequired, to operate beyond their
OL,12,Frespective jurisdictions.
