OL,3,CReview of airport policing recommended
OL,5,F"The current restrictions and
OL,6,Fgeographical limitations imposed on
OL,7,FBelfast Harbour Police and Belfast
OL,8,FInternational Airport Constabulary
OL,9,Fpresent risks for officers and the
OL,10,Fpublic and inevitable consequences for
OL,11,Fthe full and proper investigation of
OL,12,Fcrime and the transportation of people
OL,13,Funder arrest to PSNI custody
OL,14,Ffacilities. This needs to be
OL,15,Faddressed," she added.
OL,17,FBelfast Harbour Police chief officer
OL,18,FMichael Daly welcomed the report.
