OL,3,CReview of airport policing recommended
OL,5,F"While we take on board CJI's
OL,6,Frecommendation that an overarching
OL,7,Fmemorandum of understanding (MOU)
OL,8,Fshould be agreed with the PSNI, to
OL,9,Fdetail the roles and responsibilities
OL,10,Fof each police service, a number of
OL,11,Fexisting MOUs are in place and we are
OL,12,Fclear that, where relevant to Belfast
OL,13,FHarbour, our policing priorities are
OL,14,Falready closely aligned with those of
OL,15,Fthe PSNI and national standards," he
OL,16,Fsaid.
