OL,3,CReview of airport policing recommended
OL,5,F"As we implement our action plan to
OL,6,Fexecute CJI's recommendations, Belfast
OL,7,FHarbour Police remains committed to
OL,8,Fworking in partnership with all
OL,9,Frelevant bodies to continue to achieve
OL,10,Fthe highest standards of policing for
OL,11,Fthe benefit of everyone we serve.
OL,13,F"Our continued focus is on keeping the
OL,14,Fmore than 20,000 people who work here
OL,15,Fsafe and ensuring the security of the
OL,16,F760 businesses operating on Belfast
OL,17,FHarbour Estate and the 24 million
OL,18,Ftonnes of trade that comes through the
OL,19,Fport each year."
