OL,5,FPSNI Chief Superintendent Mark Roberts
OL,6,Fsaid: "We have received the Criminal
OL,7,FJustice Inspection report on 'Airport
OL,8,Fand Harbour Policing in Northern
OL,9,FIreland' and accept the small number
OL,10,Fof recommendations specific to the
OL,11,FPolice Service of Northern Ireland.
OL,13,F"Our harbours and designated airports
OL,14,Fare safe and vibrant communities which
OL,15,Fwe police in partnership with the
OL,16,FBelfast Harbour Police and Belfast
OL,17,FInternational Airport Constabulary,
OL,18,Fand we look forward to using this
OL,19,Fopportunity to develop those
OL,20,Frelationships further over the coming
OL,21,Fmonths."
